## Monte Carlo parameters

| Asset | Annual return (μ) | Annual volatility (σ) |
|---|---|---|
| Netflix NFLX | 22% | 55% |
| Nifty 50 | 12% | 18% |
| Gold ETF | 8% | 14% |

Assumes normally distributed weekly returns. This underestimates fat-tail risk — known limitation.

