## Claude API integration

```
Model:      claude-sonnet-4-20250514
Endpoint:   https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages
Max tokens: 1,000
Auth:       x-api-key header, backend only
```

Response JSON shape:
```json
{
  "headline": "...",
  "psychologyRead": "...",
  "costOfEmotion": "...",
  "blindSpot": "...",
  "strengthToLeverage": "...",
  "actionPlan": ["...", "...", "..."],
  "motivationalClose": "..."
}
```

Headline renders with a typewriter animation (30ms/char). Full fallback matrix exists for all 6 profile × decision combos.

