## Requirements and constraints

- Browser: Chrome 100+, Firefox 100+, Safari 15+, Edge 100+
- Deployment needs outbound HTTPS to `api.anthropic.com`
- No live data feeds — everything is static historical data in `marketData.js`
- Adding a new crash dataset only requires changes in `marketData.js`
- Production hardening (rate limiting, DB migrations, CI/CD) is v2.0 scope

**Performance targets:**
- Page load < 3s on 10 Mbps
- Chart animation ≥ 30 fps
- Monte Carlo median stable within ±5% across identical runs
- A new user completes a full sim in under 10 minutes

